Flora Zabelle Hitchcock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flora_Zabelle_Hitchcock 0 Flora Zabelle (April 1, 1880– October 7, 1968) was a Broadway actress who appeared in several early silent films. She was born in Constantinople, Ottoman Empire (now Istanbul, Turkey). Flora_Zabelle ( April_1 , 1880 – October_7_,_1968 ) was a_Broadway_actress who appeared in several_early_silent_films .
